{"tid":1258142,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傳保方回巢祖記做後備","createTime":"2019-06-26T03:01:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T15:51:49.000Z","uid":19552,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"3145edddad121503dbfbb4c692fe7a3d34fcdfdf","tid":1258142,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:01:16.000Z","msg":"意大利著名記者透露，一代鋼旦保方將重返祖雲達斯，擔任施捷斯尼的後備。<br />\n意大利著名足球記者迪馬斯奧（Gianluca Di Marzio），在個人網站透露名將保方（Gianluigi Buffon）即將重返祖雲達斯，更指雙方的談判十分順利，更就未來角色達成協議，暗示成事機會十分大。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n迪馬斯奧寫道：「保方和祖雲達斯絕非已成過去！」據悉，保方將擔任正選門將施捷斯尼的後備。意大利天空體育更表示保方將簽約1年，將來還會出任球隊的總監。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該41歲門將上季由祖雲達斯加盟巴黎聖日耳門，季後宣佈離隊甚至打算退休1年，不過之前也傳出他或加盟其他球會，包括英冠球隊列斯聯。"},{"pid":"6e9b1dc6bb06fce6630c2499de840a2b184bb603","tid":1258142,"uid":240613,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:03:08.000Z","msg":"咩叫退休一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab74d5ba22641aa003a952cebef4bd36101fbafd","tid":1258142,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:03:45.000Z","msg":"做臭自己個名"},{"pid":"88b14d2d9ecdc9b927dd563c36188952d565ef5a","tid":1258142,"uid":15830,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:04:07.000Z","msg":"為咗歐聯可以去到幾盡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f00277f7a390970cb7dd7e87bb352fcf2f70a07","tid":1258142,"uid":121473,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:05:12.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，好似由winning4就見你，同期果堆個個都變經典球員出番黎先買到，我要去到winning幾先見你係經典球員<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor